data.title: LibXML: Interface to Gnome libxml2 library
data.meta_description:
This module is an interface to the gnome libxml2 DOM parser (no SAX
parser support yet), and the DOM tree.  It also provides an
XML::XPath-like findnodes() interface, providing access to the XPath API
in libxml2.
data.text:
p5-XML-LibXML Interface to Gnome libxml2 library

2.0210,1 textproc =35 2.0210,1Version of this port present on the latest quarterly branch.

Maintainer: perl@FreeBSD.org

Port Added: 2001-05-29 07:40:53

Last Update: 2024-02-21 15:11:07

Commit Hash: 7428403

People watching this port, also watch:: p5-libwww, expat, unzip, libxml2, p5-XML-NamespaceSupport

Also Listed In: perl5

License: ART10 GPLv1+

WWW:

https://metacpan.org/release/XML-LibXML

Description:

This module is an interface to the gnome libxml2 DOM parser (no SAX parser support yet), and the DOM tree. It also provides an XML::XPath-like findnodes() interface, providing access to the XPath API in libxml2.

¦ ¦ ¦ ¦
